<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span><span class="c2">(الْآدَمِيّ)</span> الْإِنْسَان نِسْبَة إِلَى آدم<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
